            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Successus <lb n="2"/>Natalis <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibertus</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>maceriem <lb n="4"/>caementiciam <lb n="5"/>circa hoc tem<lb break="no" n="6"/>plum de sua pe<lb break="no" n="7"/>cunia Matro<lb break="no" n="8"/>nae ex voto sus<lb break="no" n="9"/>cepto <lb n="10"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Metadaten ergänzt nach freundlichem Hinweis von B. Amiri (2012). Z. 4: NTI-, AM-Ligatur; Z. 5: TEM-Ligatur. (B): CIL 13, 05674; Thévenard: Z. 4: caementici(a)m.</p>
